data.eml:eml: Rugosothynnus gen. nov. (Hymenoptera: Tiphiidae: Thynninae: Rhagigasterini), a newly recognised Australian genus

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Brown, Graham (2015): Rugosothynnus gen. nov. (Hymenoptera: Tiphiidae: Thynninae: Rhagigasterini), a newly recognised Australian genus. Zootaxa 3925 (3): 361-386, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3925.3.3
